    {
      "id": "insight:e7a937122206d464",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Housing shortages present distinct challenges in different urban and rural environments.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.03
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:fcd4aec88db54797",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "It's very sparse and rural. Even there, there's a housing shortage,",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 1358,
        "char_end": 1425,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 79920,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 82880,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:ae9805f84186a89a",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Baltimore's vacant housing problem is a direct consequence of historical racial redlining and purposeful disinvestment.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.09
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6e6f3dcccd53078a",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "something that I discovered when I became the mayor of Baltimore.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 4686,
        "char_end": 4751,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 231600,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 234480,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:36e5f0b6b0164bee",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "correlation to purposeful disinvestment into those neighborhoods, and all the",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 6411,
        "char_end": 6488,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 316240,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 320279,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:4283f326c0668380",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The number of vacant properties in Baltimore remained largely unchanged for two decades prior to the current administration's strategy.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.09
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:64d003c08a63f898",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "thousand vacant properties. The number essentially had not moved.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 5504,
        "char_end": 5569,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 270520,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 275080,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:1efd68c571d5d13b",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Previous administrations focused on short-term solutions for vacant housing, whereas the current strategy is a long-term, community-wide initiative.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": false,
        "insight_type": "claim"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:f4f1437b46a98b94",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "A unified strategy involving city government, state, philanthropy, and residents is essential for addressing Baltimore's housing crisis.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.39
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:d815754bc71a3996",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "that has relationships with churches and communities and mosque and",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 8714,
        "char_end": 8781,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 428760,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 432720,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:956117f487968ec9",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "philanthropic investment into the vacant strategy. So it's really everybody",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 38791,
        "char_end": 38866,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1878480,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1883080,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:821c6518307bf82b",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "State government support, including $50 million annually, has enabled significant progress in reducing vacant properties.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": false,
        "insight_type": "fact"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:ad051d8feab3d8d6",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Many vacant properties in Baltimore are privately owned, posing challenges for city intervention and redevelopment.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.18
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:6077190451f9dfca",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "city of Baltimore are not owned by the City of Baltimore.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 10577,
        "char_end": 10634,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 521039,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 524000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:75deaa02cb573faf",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "They're owned by private folks who are sitting on them,",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 10645,
        "char_end": 10700,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 524159,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 526520,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:981fe297bfac18a4",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The process of acquiring and renovating vacant properties is lengthy and complex, often requiring court intervention.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "fact",
        "position_hint": 0.28
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:899d677c5bf433a6",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "worked with the court. We have a special inrim docket,",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 17296,
        "char_end": 17350,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 839559,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 842040,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:88e92de7ee1bf9fa",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Baltimore's strategy involves block-level planning to tailor redevelopment to specific neighborhood needs and aesthetics.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.34
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:3900ad99ddb7853c",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 5: in the game. That's where the block by block comes. Okay, really,",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 15275,
        "char_end": 15351,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 746080,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 748680,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:bdc866ff8316612a",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 5: neighborhoods love their neighborhood aesthetic and they want to keep",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 25346,
        "char_end": 25426,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1247000,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1250480,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:9963e8c384b5d019",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Speaker 5: neighborhood strategic investment areas, identifying those things before we get",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 21899,
        "char_end": 21989,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1067480,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1073000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:5b4b2a3d6e49e405",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The city is using Tax Increment Financing (TIF) for non-contiguous areas, an innovative approach to incentivize development in disinvested neighborhoods.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": false,
        "insight_type": "claim"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:0a0df835df5cdf2b",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "Baltimore's revitalization efforts are strategically focused on historically redlined and disinvested areas.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": true,
        "insight_type": "claim",
        "position_hint": 0.2
      },
      "confidence": 1.0
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:661c20126a1f2b53",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "even the vacant smap today, it's the same neighborhoods, literally",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 5955,
        "char_end": 6021,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 293360,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 297560,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:41ea0c690cd127b4",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "correlation to purposeful disinvestment into those neighborhoods, and all the",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 6411,
        "char_end": 6488,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 316240,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 320279,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "quote:91645e44dc5e1cd4",
      "type": "Quote",
      "properties": {
        "text": "been disinvested in in the butterfly or the red line neighborhoods.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "speaker_id": null,
        "char_start": 24093,
        "char_end": 24160,
        "timestamp_start_ms": 1172240,
        "timestamp_end_ms": 1176000,
        "transcript_ref": "transcripts/0001 - How Baltimore_s Mayor Is Fighting the City_s Vacant Housing Crisis_20260506-135048_ba02775e.txt"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "insight:bfb2db9a6f8811c8",
      "type": "Insight",
      "properties": {
        "text": "The city aims to balance private development and profit with the goal of improving neighborhoods and providing affordable housing.",
        "episode_id": "653bb844-d3b0-425e-9e28-b43e00ee5196",
        "grounded": false,
        "insight_type": "claim"
      }
    }
